@node Req "HNet V1.0: Requirements"

@{b}What you need to run HNet:@{ub}

* Two Amigas. (No network with one, just a Notwork!)

* A cable (serial).

* Amiga OS 2.0 or higher.
  Only tested with 3.0, but it should work...

@endnode

@node Lim "HNet V1.0: Limitations"

@{b}Things that don`t work...@{ub}

* No file transfer program

* No support for SANA2

* No settings program

The next release will have a settings editor and a file transfer tool.

@endnode

